title: #120: Shroomfest 2013 (@MatEdgar, @PeteeC, @TonyHinchcliffe)
itunes:title: Shroomfest 2013 with Mat Edgar, Tony Hinchcliffe, Pete C
description: Tony Hinchcliffe, Mat Edgar, Pete Cornacchione, and I spent Shroomfest together this year. We drove out to Joshua Tree, ate some shrooms, and wandered out into the wilderness. And then we had, what I believe, is probably the first podcast recorded at Joshua Tree National Park.
